To run the SCF calculation.

1) Prepare the input file and name it with the extension '.in'

2) This can be done by using the GUI --> pwgui

*** An input file has been included for reference.

3) Then after the creation of the input file, run the SCF by using the following command.

	pw.x < Cu.scf.in > Cu.scf.out

4) Here the output is generated and printed in the file 'Cu.scf.out'

		***************************

PS: Depending on your machine, please include the mpirun before the above command.
    The general mpirun command looks like the following:

			mpirun -np 4 

    Followed by the above command.

